description: This module provides a method to work with the Inferelator algorithm from the Baliga Lab at the Institute for Systems Biology. The Inferelator algorithm infers regulatory networks from gene expression data, and takes as input cMonkey biclusters, a list of regulators, and expression data.
name: Module Inferelator Version 1.0
organization: Office of Scientific and Technical Information (OSTI)
